Package polimi.ingsw.listener

Class ListenersHandler

java.lang.Object
polimi.ingsw.listener.ListenersHandler
public class ListenersHandler extends Object
The ListenersHandler class is responsible for managing a List of GameListener GameListener
and for notifying the view when a change occurs in the GameModel GameModel.
When notifying an event, we need to pass the GameModelImmutable GameModelImmutable to the view to have access to the updated GameModel.
